prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, crooked party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch and struggling hilariously to blow a single, uncooperative party horn that is dangling just out of reach. Below the sloth, the words "happy birthday" are elegantly written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a vibrant watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures and foliage, capturing a lighthearted and funny moment.
